dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90d76933109dbaf6499e8088322713bf0c61917f","tid":1067122,"uid":53065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a4b2cb07eeabccef4a370e68f2c73e7324229d9","tid":1067122,"uid":127522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d80276a75cb2f4496caf129d736d53775ed729a7","tid":1067122,"uid":53065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T10:36:34.000Z","msg":"升級要加幾多？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T10:46:47.000Z","msg":"2800HKD"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T11:14:21.000Z","msg":"咁真係唔錯啵！本身張機票幾錢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T11:17:26.000Z","msg":"13000 (Premium Economy)加2000 Air NZ Economy"},{"pid":"149dfd4537a2c4009599b9d206077c19ad5b4ecb","tid":1067122,"uid":32464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T11:19:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa131ee5e03da1f33138f3b1cd4aa2099f9d352","tid":1067122,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d80276a75cb2f4496caf129d736d53775ed729a7","tid":1067122,"uid":53065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0ba26d3ecbe3624733eb1374fd54f6f0ba38b2c5","tid":1067122,"uid":127522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"de37f6c6ed427b563e8a709a72fbc77dedb42a43","tid":1067122,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T10:15:42.000Z","msg":"Day 0<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong -  Melbourne <br />\n拎到大假去紐西蘭，為左要就Cook Island 航班，紐西蘭採用南島入北島出，再去Cook Island，第一站係南島最大城市Christchurch (基督城)，而呢一次用澳洲航空經Melbourne 去<br />\n<br />\n等上機<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WrR3wsH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWrR3wsH.jpg&h=8bdb4d6d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T10:19:08.000Z","msg":"今日航班係用澳洲航空最新嘅787-9， 今日又好好彩咁樣有一個幾好嘅價錢可以升級去Business Class<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wbip0np.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWbip0np.jpg&h=620cf764&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T10:36:34.000Z","msg":"升級要加幾多？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T20:42:19.000Z","msg":"值得一提既係今次採用嘅飛機係澳洲航空 為紀念原住民貢獻既特別塗裝，機身花紋 靈感係源自原住民嘅甘薯"},{"pid":"49b42e2e9a5fdcdd3c8fd45a6e025c5335423224","tid":1067122,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T22:04:23.000Z","msg":"Day 1 <br />\nMelbourne &gt; Christchurch (City Sightseeing)<br />\n<br />\n人係Melbourne, 講小小第11-12日會去既Cook Islands, 應該無咩人去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/35/Flag_of_the_Cook_Islands.svg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F3%2F35%2FFlag_of_the_Cook_Islands.svg&h=2b376576&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n庫克群島（英語：Cook Islands）是一個位在南太平洋上，介於法屬玻里尼西亞與斐濟之間，由15個島嶼組成的群島，其命名起源於遠征探索南太平洋，發現了許多島嶼的詹姆斯&middot;庫克船長，與紐西蘭之間存在自由聯合關係的聯繫國，也是大英國協王國當中紐西蘭王國的構成部份。庫克群島，被聯合國認可具有外交締約能力，並參加了世界衛生組織等國際機構。<br />\n整個群島原則上分為南北兩個集團。其中，南集團佔有全國240平方公里的國土中，約90%的面積，包括首都阿瓦魯阿所在的最大島拉羅東加島（Rarotonga Is.）在內的九個島嶼都屬於此集團，大部分都是火山活動造成的島嶼，土壤肥沃、熱帶植被滿布。至於北集團則大都是距離海平面沒多高、由珊瑚礁構成的低矮環礁，島上植被零星，通常中央會有大型的潟湖。 雖然土地面積狹小，但是由庫克群島周圍所構成的經濟海域範圍，卻多達兩百萬平方公里，因此漁業資源對該群島的經濟佔有非常高比例的重要性。"},{"pid":"641e74a21dcff9cf15a12e87bd5e113febb6b284","tid":1067122,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49b42e2e9a5fdcdd3c8fd45a6e025c5335423224","tid":1067122,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T22:04:23.000Z","msg":"Day 1 <br />\nMelbourne &gt; Christchurch (City Sightseeing)<br />\n<br />\n人係Melbourne, 講小小第11-12日會去既Cook Islands, 應該無咩人去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/35/Flag_of_the_Cook_Islands.svg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F3%2F35%2FFlag_of_the_Cook_Islands.svg&h=2b376576&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n庫克群島（英語：Cook Islands）是一個位在南太平洋上，介於法屬玻里尼西亞與斐濟之間，由15個島嶼組成的群島，其命名起源於遠征探索南太平洋，發現了許多島嶼的詹姆斯&middot;庫克船長，與紐西蘭之間存在自由聯合關係的聯繫國，也是大英國協王國當中紐西蘭王國的構成部份。庫克群島，被聯合國認可具有外交締約能力，並參加了世界衛生組織等國際機構。<br />\n整個群島原則上分為南北兩個集團。其中，南集團佔有全國240平方公里的國土中，約90%的面積，包括首都阿瓦魯阿所在的最大島拉羅東加島（Rarotonga Is.）在內的九個島嶼都屬於此集團，大部分都是火山活動造成的島嶼，土壤肥沃、熱帶植被滿布。至於北集團則大都是距離海平面沒多高、由珊瑚礁構成的低矮環礁，島上植被零星，通常中央會有大型的潟湖。 雖然土地面積狹小，但是由庫克群島周圍所構成的經濟海域範圍，卻多達兩百萬平方公里，因此漁業資源對該群島的經濟佔有非常高比例的重要性。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T22:07:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.worldatlas.com/img/areamap/nonav/cookisloceania.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldatlas.com%2Fimg%2Fareamap%2Fnonav%2Fcookisloceania.png&h=53cf8365&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b0fff1f7bb4878cf4aa46f6e2966a2ced3b1191","tid":1067122,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T23:54:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tiRbKUo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtiRbKUo.jpg&h=a0b7f923&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又等上機 QF133 Melbourne - Christchurch"},{"pid":"ad972f1d2621926fcd93b77f1f1126613eb5d014","tid":1067122,"uid":127522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T07:12:11.000Z","msg":"人終於到左Christchurch 班機準時1709到, 用左10分鐘清關，第一餐去又平又好食既Nandos<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dvk0FET.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdvk0FET.jpg&h=7db9583a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以前係澳洲住成日食，可惜香港無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f01693c2d3521295c8892aac04a5f03bbd3d8c0","tid":1067122,"uid":127522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"318ffaf9f8a2c81746dec3e93dd33ca5108416e7","tid":1067122,"uid":202735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T10:34:51.000Z","msg":"人在紐西蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T07:31:48.000Z","msg":"